description: This file defines a data model for movie scripts using Pydantic, sets up an agent for generating movie scripts in JSON mode, and includes example usage comments.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script, including setting, ending, genre, name, characters, and storyline.
